_sText:
Hello there, this is my latest map of 2007 called cs_resort

This is a hostage rescue map set in a resort, during the night.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Features:

Mini Elevator
Pool
Vents
HDR lighting

----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Update 4!

- Added more detail to the pool and added some cover.

- Added more props and decals.

- Vents are now bigger, so you can now run in them.

- New Nav file from Chizbone.

Feel free to leave comments and advise, as I still wish to make this map better for players to enjoy.

Thankyou
